nodes.text: TK-420 was the designation of a Human Imperial stormtrooper serving in an inspection crew during the Galactic Civil War. TK-420 was tasked with examining supply shipments to the Death Star battlestation. The trooper wore the standard suit of stormtrooper armor, and wielded an E-11 blaster rifle.
TK-420 was created by a card for the Premiere set of Decipher's 2001 Jedi Knights Trading Card Game.
